                                <p><span class="whatwedotitile">8. Compensation and Benefits</span></p>
                                <p class="text-justify">Creating competitive compensation and benefits packages is critical to attracting and retaining talent. Striking the right balance between offering attractive perks and maintaining financial sustainability requires strategic planning. Transparent communication about compensation policies also plays a key role in employee satisfaction and retention.</p>
        
